{"type": "article", "id": 29493, "title": "与健身球结合的办公椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-12T23:01:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160712160817BY9qWZpSDnEocNz1.png", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>长时间坐在办公桌前的你或许明白久坐对于腰背造成的损伤，纽约时报健康记者 Gretchen Reynolds 就曾<a href=\"http://well.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/10/09/ask-well-when-sitting-can-be-good-for-you/\" rel=\"nofollow\">表示</a>“坐本身并没有坏处，问题是坐着不动”，这也为 Darren Mark 提供了灵感。他将健身球和符合人体工程学的座椅合二为一，设计出了一把能让人在坐着的同时进行活动的办公椅 <a href=\"http://www.sprangchair.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Språng</a>。健身球被固定在底座和坐垫之间，提供的弹力可以让人坐在上面小幅活动，一定程度上也能缓解工作压力。坐下时背部可以倚靠在由关节构成的椅背上，更贴近腰部的位置可以改善不正确的坐姿并且缓解背部的不适感。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/sprangchair/the-sprang-chair-the-perfect-balance-of-movement-a\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 350 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712161031WAbT02PfYutsLpr6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.550000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712161031UApn0g6SiLxkyD24.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208824\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712161032XEkytZFPl4nujNvY.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.616176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712161031gCufc5V9jGqTlKtN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}